Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.92,0:03:04.84,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}重叠在手掌之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.02,0:03:08.45,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}今を変えることは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.02,0:03:08.45,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}改变现在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:11.94,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}辛いこともあるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:11.94,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}虽然是件痛苦的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:15.87,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}たとえピースが揃っても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:15.87,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}就算Piece全部集齐
