Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.87,0:03:18.89,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}也得用这双手去指引
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.91,0:03:21.61,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}大事な今を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.91,0:03:21.61,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}把重要的现在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:25.08,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}手放すのは怖いよね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:25.08,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}放手离去是很可怕的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:30.65,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}でも待ち望んだ全ては
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:30.65,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}但是期待的一切
